<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glow-vi">glow <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡləʊ/    美 /ɡloʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1vi">1.<strong>vi 发出微弱而稳定的光；(脸等部位) 发热；发红：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The beside lamp glowed softly.
床头灯发出柔和的光。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His face <strong>glowed with</strong> delight.
他高兴得红光满面。</p></div></div>